&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role requires extensive travel (up to 90%) across the U.S., Canada, and Mexico, and candidates must reside near a major airport to support frequent travel needs.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
